{{cite web|url=http://www.wnd.com/index.php?fa=PAGE.view&pageId=93372 |title=You can't keep a good Tea Party down! |publisher=Wnd.com |date= |accessdate=2009-10-18}}</ref>，但节目并没有引用她提到的最早的15亿美元的数字电视机顶盒推广项目是在2005年得到批准的<ref name="Rakovich"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/PLAW-109publ171/html/PLAW-109publ171.htm |title=DEFICIT REDUCTION ACT OF 2005, SEC. 3005|accessdate=2010-02-12}}</ref>。

