</ref><ref name="jenkins mar14">
{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/search-results/m/21987028/a-2009-tea-party.htm|title=A 2009 Tea Party|accessdate=2009-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422004946/http://www.foxnews.com/search-results/m/21987028/a-2009-tea-party.htm|archivedate=2009-04-22}}</ref>。
